 <title>Raccontare la chimica: modi, mezzi e creatività</title>
 <link>http://www.palermoscienza.it/news/raccontare-la-chimica-modi-mezzi-e-creativit%C3%A0</link>
 <description>&lt;div style=&quot;font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;L&amp;#39;associazione PALERMOSCIENZA, in collaborazione con YOCOCU, Università &amp;quot;La Sapienza&amp;quot; di Roma e UNIPA, organizzano&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;ChimicArte&lt;/strong&gt;, un corso di&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;divulgazione della chimica&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;attraverso i beni culturali.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;Il corso si svolgerà a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Palermo&lt;/strong&gt;, dal&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;21 al 25 settembre 2015&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;presso il dipartimento STEBICEF - ed.17 - Viale delle Scienze, ed ha un&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial&quot; size=&quot;2&quot;&gt;costo di&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;80 euro&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;per chi si iscrive entro il 20 maggio e di&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;110 euro&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;dopo tale data.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;Le iscrizioni si chiuderanno il&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;27 giugno 2015&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;e sono ammessi&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;massimo 25 corsisti&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;Per gli iscritti a PALERMOSCIENZA, YOCOCU, Chimici per un&amp;#39;ora, Università degli Studi di Palermo e insegnanti degli Istituti Scolastici è previsto uno&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;sconto di 15 euro&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;&quot;&gt;Altri dettagli &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.palermoscienza.it/system/files/corso%20divulgazione%20chimica%20palermo.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;qui&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/div&gt;
